'how could they have launched these missiles", 'start': 38.52, 'duration': 3.7}, {'text': "very quickly, if needed, but also never by accident?'", 'start': 42.32, 'duration': 4.28}, {'text': 'So I visited one of these Titan missile silos
in the Arizona desert', 'start': 46.88, 'duration': 3.8}, {'text': 'to find out exactly what it would have taken

ever deployed by the United States.', 'start': 76.42, 'duration': 5.9}, {'text': 'And what kind of bomb is in there?', 'start': 82.52, 'duration': 1.46}, {'text': 'That is a thermonuclear bomb.', 'start': 84.08, 'duration': 1.94}, {'text': 'It is a 9 megaton weapon.', 'start': 86.28, 'duration': 1.56}, {'text': 'Compared to Hiroshima?', 'start': 88.04, 'duration': 1.6}, {'text': 'Oh, call it 650 times.', 'start': 89.88, 'duration': 3.08}, {'text': 'An enormously powerful weapon.', 'start': 93.62, 'duration': 2.16}, {'text': 'And what was the idea with it?', 'start': 96.2, 'duration': 1.82}, {'text': 'The idea behind Titan II was to instill

Laboratory in Pasadena, California.", 'start': 7.91, 'duration': 5.57}, {'text': 'How many moons can you see this month?', 'start': 13.48, 'duration': 2.52}, {'text': 'Our moon is easy to see, but the others will
take a little magnification.', 'start': 16.0, 'duration': 5.08}, {'text': "Jupiter's four Galilean moons can be spotted
with a pair of steady binoculars but really", 'start': 21.08, 'duration': 5.35}, {'text': 'shine through a telescope.', 'start': 26.43, 'duration': 2.3}, {'text': 'You might be able to see the different sizes
of the four moons like what Galileo saw and', 'start': 28.73, 'duration': 4.89}, {'text': 'sketched over 400 years ago.', 'start': 33.62, 'duration': 2.959}, {'text': 'And this is a great month to view Jupiter.', 'start': 36.579, 'duration': 2.39}, {'text': 'It reaches opposition on October 28 when the
king of the planets is closest to Earth in', 'start': 38.969, 'duration': 5.201}, {'text': 'its orbit around the sun and best-placed for
viewing.', 'start': 44.17, 'duration': 3.86}, {'text': "If you haven't seen Jupiter through a telescope,
join your nearest amateur astronomy club or", 'start': 48.03, 'duration': 4.86}, {'text': 'observatory on their monthly public nights
and have a look!', 'start': 52.89, 'duration': 4.3}, {'text': "Last fall Jupiter's south equatorial belt
dramatically disappeared.", 'start': 57.19, 'duration': 5.48}, {'text': 'This year the clouds that obscured it are
gone, and the familiar reddish belt and the', 'start': 62.67, 'duration': 4.74}, {'text': 'famous Great Red Spot are prominent once again.', 'start': 67.41, 'duration': 4.76}, {'text': 'What other planetary moons are on display?', 'start': 72.17, 'duration': 3.09}, {'text': 'Both Neptune and Uranus are low in the southern
sky this month, just after sunset.', 'start': 75.26, 'duration': 5.5}, {'text': "You'll need a big and powerful telescope to
spot their moons, though.", 'start': 80.76, 'duration': 4.74}, {'text': 'It might be easier to look at photos of these
moons taken by astrophotographers or sketches', 'start': 85.5, 'duration': 5.24}, {'text': 'of objects seen through the eyepiece of a
telescope.', 'start': 90.74, 'duration': 3.21}, {'text': 'Mark October 8 on your calendars.', 'start': 93.95, 'duration': 2.87}, {'text': 'That special night is both International Observe
the Moon night and the peak of the Draconid', 'start': 96.82, 'duration': 5.28}, {'text': 'meteor shower.', 'start': 102.1, 'duration': 1.43}, {'text': "Unfortunately, you can't have your cake -- or
your green cheese -- and eat it, too.", 'start': 103.53, 'duration': 5.15}, {'text': 'Moonlight interferes with both the Draconids
on the 8th and the Orionids later in the month.', 'start': 108.68, 'duration': 6.41}, {'text': 'Europe gets the best view of the Draconids.', 'start': 115.09, 'duration': 2.61}, {'text': "But maybe you'll see a few Orionids closer
to the end of the month.", 'start': 117.7, 'duration': 3.82}, {'text': 'They peak on the 21st.', 'start': 121.52, 'duration': 1.4}, {'text': 'You can read about moons of the solar system
at solarsystem.nasa.gov/yss for Year of the', 'start': 122.92, 'duration': 8.009}, {'text': 'Solar System.', 'start': 130.929, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': "And you can learn about all of NASA's missions
at www.nasa.gov", 'start': 131.929, 'duration': 5.28}, {'text': "That's all for this month.", 'start': 137.209, 'duration': 1.01}, {'text': "I'm Jane Houston Jones.", 'start': 138.219, 'duration': 1.291}]

[{'text': "Hi I'm Christy Wilhelmi from Gardenerd and
today I'm going to show you how to take care", 'start': 6.879, 'duration': 3.72}, {'text': 'of your tools.', 'start': 10.599, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': 'A good pair of pruning shears can you a lifetime
if you know how to take care of it properly.', 'start': 11.599, 'duration': 5.491}, {'text': "Cleaning, getting all the sap off, disinfecting,
sharpening, oiling, it's all part of garden", 'start': 17.09, 'duration': 6.069}, {'text': 'care for your tools.', 'start': 23.159, 'duration': 2.071}, {'text': "So I'm going to show you how.", 'start': 25.23, 'duration': 1.67}, {'text': 'These are Felco Pruners.', 'start': 26.9, 'duration': 2.529}, {'text': "They're a really good quality pruning shear
and they have a sharp edge on one side and", 'start': 29.429, 'duration': 6.301}, {'text': 'then the rest of the points are not sharp.', 'start': 35.73, 'duration': 2.7}, {'text': 'Most of the time...you can see this is covered
with crap and it needs cleaning, and there', 'start': 38.43, 'duration': 4.5}, {'text': 'are a couple things you can do to clean.', 'start': 42.93, 'duration': 2.73}, {'text': "The most available resource is this, you know,
sanding block, but it's not really the best", 'start': 45.66, 'duration': 7.42}, {'text': 'one.', 'start': 53.08, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': 'If you want to make your life really easy,
the Sandflex hand block is the way to go.', 'start': 54.08, 'duration': 4.46}, {'text': 'This thing is a miracle, and use the medium
course one for that.', 'start': 58.54, 'duration': 4.47}, {'text': "And basically what you're going to do is use
the sand block to scrub.", 'start': 63.01, 'duration': 4.95}, {'text': "It just makes it go away, it's amazing.", 'start': 67.96, 'duration': 2.969}, {'text': "You'll see.", 'start': 70.929, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': 'I mean just look at it, you can already see
it just disappearing.', 'start': 71.929, 'duration': 3.391}, {'text': 'To disinfect your tools you want to use alcohol
or a bleach solution.', 'start': 75.32, 'duration': 5.03}, {'text': "You can dip it straight into alcohol and then
wipe it clean, and that's something that you", 'start': 80.35, 'duration': 4.059}, {'text': "should do especially if you've been pruning
something that has a disease.", 'start': 84.409, 'duration': 4.14}, {'text': "You're supposed to dip your pruners in between
each cut, but that's for a pruning video some", 'start': 88.549, 'duration': 5.18}, {'text': 'other day.', 'start': 93.729, 'duration': 1.34}, {'text': "Once you're done disinfecting your tools,
it's a good idea to oil them so they don't", 'start': 95.069, 'duration': 4.91}, {'text': 'rust.', 'start': 99.979, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': 'Now some people recommend using a household
kitchen oil spray, like Pam or something like', 'start': 100.979, 'duration': 4.831}, {'text': 'that, but I feel like it goes rancid too quickly.', 'start': 105.81, 'duration': 3.47}, {'text': "I'd rather use something appropriate for pruners.", 'start': 109.28, 'duration': 2.03}, {'text': 'So you can use WD-40 or I recommend using
a pruner oil which is specifically made for', 'start': 111.31, 'duration': 7.449}, {'text': 'gardening tools.', 'start': 118.759, 'duration': 1.391}, {'text': 'So what you do, and this stuff does smell
like machine oil.', 'start': 120.15, 'duration': 5.179}, {'text': 'So you apply a thin coat to the blades and
you also want to apply a thin coat to the', 'start': 125.329, 'duration': 14.411}, {'text': 'spring.', 'start': 139.74, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': 'Take the spring off and clean the gunk out
of that and then oil it as well.', 'start': 140.74, 'duration': 5.05}, {'text': "Once you've done that, let it sit for a couple
of minutes and then wipe it completely clean,", 'start': 145.79, 'duration': 5.65}, {'text': 'reassemble put the spring back on and good
as new.', 'start': 151.44, 'duration': 4.71}, {'text': "Now if you want to sharpen your tools it's
great to have a hand file on hand like this.", 'start': 156.15, 'duration': 6.07}, {'text': 'This is a Corona hand file and it basically
has a little tiny whetstone attached to the', 'start': 162.22, 'duration': 5.98}, {'text': 'end of a handle, which makes it easy to sharpen
your tools without having to take them apart.', 'start': 168.2, 'duration': 5.22}, {'text': 'So basically you want to follow the bevel
of the blade on the same angle, which is like', 'start': 173.42, 'duration': 4.73}, {'text': 'a 33-45 degree angle.', 'start': 178.15, 'duration': 3.6}, {'text': 'And you want to make 3-4 strokes along the
edge of the blade and once you do that you', 'start': 181.75, 'duration': 7.98}, {'text': 'flip it over and run one flat to remove the
burrs.', 'start': 189.73, 'duration': 3.44}, {'text': "And that's it.", 'start': 193.17, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': 'Pretty straight forward.', 'start': 194.17, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': "If you do this with your tools, they'll last
for years and years, and they will be worth", 'start': 195.17, 'duration': 5.36}, {'text': 'every penny and every second of time you spend
cleaning them.', 'start': 200.53, 'duration': 2.79}, {'text': 'If you want to learn more about cleaning your
tools and gardening and all this kind of stuff', 'start': 203.32, 'duration': 6.28}, {'text': 'that you love as a Gardenerd, visit Gardenerd.com.', 'start': 209.6, 'duration': 2.75}, {'text': 'And if you like this video, like, subscribe
and share it with your friends.', 'start': 212.35, 'duration': 3.61}, {'text': 'Happy Gardening.', 'start': 215.96, 'duration': 0.52}]
